You are here: SALESFORCE HELP > DOCS > ANALYTICS > Schedule Data Refresh for a CRM Analytics Template

Schedule the app creation process includes data assets that import the latest data to CRM Analytics. Schedule the app to be refreshed every day to ensure that your app uses up-to-date data.

From Setup, enter App Install History, and select App Install History. Find your app in the list of installed apps. Click the dropdown arrow  to schedule a refresh. Pick the days you want and set a time for refreshing the app data. It's best to select a time outside normal working hours so the data refresh doesn't interrupt business activities.

The data refresh for your app now runs every day at the time you set.
